<DocSection Title="Zero Configuration Magic" Icon="✨">
    <p>BlazzyMotion uses <strong>Source Generators</strong> to automatically create item templates from your data models.</p>

    <div class="bz-callout">
        <strong>How it works:</strong> When you mark a property with <code>[BzImage]</code>, the Source Generator creates a registration function at compile-time.
    </div>
</DocSection>

<DocSection Title="Step 1: Define Your Model" Icon="1️⃣">
    <p>Create a model class and mark the image property with <code>[BzImage]</code>:</p>

    <CodeBlock Language="csharp" Code="@_step1Code" />
</DocSection>

<DocSection Title="Step 2: Use the Component" Icon="2️⃣">
    <p>Just pass your items to the component:</p>

    <CodeBlock Language="razor" Code="@_step2Code" />
</DocSection>

